"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-06-08-bankrupt-olympic-hero-bradley-wiggins-considers-making-heartbreaking-decision-20996118\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Cycling legendSir Bradley Wigginshas been declared bankrupt and could be forced to hand over his medals and trophies as his financial difficulties continue to mount.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cycling legendSir Bradley\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 25}, {\"ngram\": \"Wigginshas\", \"from\": 26, \"to\": 36}, {\"ngram\": \"his medals\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 103}, {\"ngram\": \"trophies\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"his financial difficulties\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiggins, who retired from the sport in 2016 after a decorated career, has racked up huge amounts of debt with numerous business ventures over the years.\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiggins\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"a decorated career\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"huge amounts\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"debt\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous business ventures\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiggins Rights Limited, a company owned by \\u00adWiggins, his former wife Cath and his mother Linda, entered liquidation in 2020 with debts amounting to \\u00a3650,000.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5598411004968894e-25, \"text\": \"Wiggins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\"}, {\"begin\": 390, \"end\": 394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CATH_database\", \"score\": 0.9999999998635758, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cath\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CATH_database\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CATH_database\"}, {\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McMahon\", \"score\": 0.9749385570258069, \"rank\": 0.02570539715845136, \"text\": \"Linda\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McMahon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McMahon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiggins Rights Limited\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"a company\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"his former wife\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"his mother\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"liquidation\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"debts\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just two years later, the 44-year-old was placed in an \\u00adIndividual Voluntary Arrangement to help him pay off creditors, including HM \\u00adRevenue & Customs.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an \\u00adIndividual Voluntary Arrangement\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"creditors\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"HM\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"Customs\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, by November last year, the debt had spiralled to almost \\u00a31 million, in part due to an outstanding director's loan which Wiggins previously disputed.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"the debt\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"an outstanding director's loan\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiggins\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With little progress made in the months following, Wiggins has now officially been declared bankrupt, according toThe Times,after a hearing at Lancaster county court on June 3.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 844, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5598411004968894e-25, \"text\": \"Wiggins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"little progress\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"the months\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"toThe Times\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"a hearing\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"Lancaster county court\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cyclist had already put the rights to the trademarks of his own name, 'Wiggins' and 'Wiggo', up for sale but a trustee will now be appointed to seize Wiggins' assets and help pay back debts.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5598411004968894e-25, \"text\": \"Wiggins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cyclist\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"the rights\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"the trademarks\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"his own name\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiggins\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"'Wiggo\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"sale\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"a trustee\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"debts\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That could mean the Englishman has to hand over Olympic medals and Tour de France trophies and even his Sports Personality of the Year award.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999995736653545, \"rank\": 2.3527897183063804e-07, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Englishman\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"trophies\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"even his Sports Personality\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the Year award\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiggins is yet to comment publicly on the latest development.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wiggins\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest development\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over a lengthy career, Wiggins became one of the most decorated cyclists in British history.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_British_Isles\", \"score\": 0.995667357529881, \"rank\": 0.004351495946360553, \"text\": \"British history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_British_Isles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_British_Isles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lengthy career\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiggins\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"the most decorated cyclists\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Winning his first Olympic medal at the 2000 Sydney Games, he went on to win seven further medals, including five golds.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2000 Sydney Games\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"seven further medals\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"five golds\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2012, Wiggins's crowning achievement came at the Tour de France when he claimed the Yellow Jersey to become the first Briton to ever win the race.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1597, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5598411004968894e-25, \"text\": \"Wiggins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\"}, {\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yellow Jersey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tour de France\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Briton\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He followed that up just months later by winning gold in the Road time trial at the 2012 London Games.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the Road time trial\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 London Games\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such achievements saw Wiggins win that year's BBC Sports Personality of the Year Award and receive a knighthood in the 2013 New Years Honours.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.999887092564553, \"rank\": 0.00011210171542286531, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Such achievements\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiggins\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"the Year Award\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"a knighthood\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2013 New Years Honours\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He came back four years later to win his final Olympic medal - yet another gold - in the Team pursuit in Rio de Janeiro before retiring in December 2016.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2091, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.303451860760003e-13, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his final Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the Team pursuit\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having retired from cycling, he began making the transition into indoor rowing with one eye on competition for Britain at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2252, \"end\": 2259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999827660224444, \"rank\": 1.6456794837842367e-05, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"the transition\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"indoor rowing\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"one eye\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, such aspirations never came to fruition, with Wiggins announcing in 2018 that he would no longer be training professionally for the sport.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such aspirations\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"fruition\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiggins\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former cyclist has embarked on a number of other careers since retiring.\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The former cyclist\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"other careers\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He undertook a degree in social work at the Open University, while he also briefly funded a professional development cycling team - Team Wiggins - to help bring through the next generation of riders.\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2554, \"end\": 2569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Open_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999988735908, \"rank\": 1.1265385437943983e-09, \"text\": \"Open University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Open_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Open_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a degree\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"social work\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional development cycling team\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"riders\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, sporting stars declaring bankruptcy is not uncommon.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sporting stars\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"bankruptcy\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to The Times, Paul Rouse, head of client services at the accountancy firm Forvis Mazars, said: 'As you would expect, those involved in elite sport are often focussed solely on their primary goals of winning titles and striving for sporting excellence.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 3040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2792, \"end\": 2801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"score\": 0.9999998964558525, \"rank\": 1.035441575795697e-07, \"text\": \"The Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paul Rouse\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"client services\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"the accountancy firm Forvis Mazars\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sport\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"their primary goals\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2984}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting excellence\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Professionals will surround them to advise on the financial benefits that follow that success, and they would be wise to ensure that their chosen advisors are trustworthy, and that they are safeguarding their client's long-term position.'\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Professionals\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3056}, {\"ngram\": \"the financial benefits\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3111}, {\"ngram\": \"that success\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3136}, {\"ngram\": \"their chosen advisors\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3197}, {\"ngram\": \"their client's long-term position\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former Premier League footballers Craig Bellamy and Wes Brown were declared bankrupt in recent years, while tennis star Boris Becker was ordered to hand over his Wimbledon trophies after his bankruptcy in 2022.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3317, \"end\": 3330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.782214669382682e-29, \"text\": \"Craig Bellamy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\"}, {\"begin\": 3335, \"end\": 3344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wes_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.491285824853493e-23, \"text\": \"Wes Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wes_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wes_Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 3403, \"end\": 3415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boris Becker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Former Premier League footballers\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram